---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<div class="page-container">
		<div class="page-header">
			<h1>Disclaimer and Editorial Disclosure</h1>
			<p class="last-updated">Last Updated: April 17, 2026</p>
		</div>

		<div class="page-content">
			<p>
				Welcome to Akboheim. This Disclaimer and Editorial Disclosure applies to akboheim.com and governs all content published on this website. By accessing and using this website, you acknowledge and agree to the terms outlined below.
			</p>

			<section id="about-akboheim">
				<h2>ABOUT AKBOHEIM</h2>
				<p>
					Akboheim is an online editorial platform dedicated to culture, literature, and education. We are based in Miami, Florida. Our mission is to provide insightful commentary, analysis, reviews, and educational content to our readers. Unless otherwise stated, all opinions expressed on this website are those of the respective authors and do not necessarily reflect the views of Akboheim as an organization.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section id="editorial-independence">
				<h2>EDITORIAL INDEPENDENCE</h2>
				<p>
					Akboheim maintains full editorial independence. Our writers and editors operate independently from our advertising and business development teams. Sponsored content, when published, will always be clearly identified and disclosed to our readers.
				</p>
				<p>
					We do not allow advertisers to influence our editorial content. Advertisements displayed on our website are separate from our editorial content, and we do not endorse any products or services advertised unless explicitly stated.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section id="advertising-disclosure">
				<h2>ADVERTISING DISCLOSURE</h2>
				<p>
					This website participates in the Google AdSense program and may display third-party advertisements. These advertisements are served by Google and its partner networks. Akboheim does not control the specific advertisements that appear on our website.
				</p>
				<p>
					Google AdSense uses cookies to serve ads based on your prior visits to our website and other websites on the Internet. For more information about how Google uses data when you use our website, please visit: <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites</a>
				</p>
				<p>
					We do not endorse any of the products or services advertised on our website through Google AdSense or any other advertising program. The presence of an advertisement on our website does not constitute an endorsement, sponsorship, or recommendation by Akboheim.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section id="affiliate-disclosure">
				<h2>AFFILIATE DISCLOSURE</h2>
				<p>
					Akboheim may participate in affiliate marketing programs, which means we may earn commissions on purchases made through our links to retailer sites. When you click on an affiliate link and make a purchase, we may receive a small commission at no additional cost to you.
				</p>
				<p>
					Whenever we include affiliate links in our content, we will disclose this relationship clearly within the article or page. Our editorial integrity is paramount, and we only recommend products, books, or services that we genuinely believe will be of value to our readers.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section id="accuracy-of-information">
				<h2>ACCURACY OF INFORMATION</h2>
				<p>
					While we strive to provide accurate, up-to-date, and reliable information, Akboheim makes no representations or warranties of any kind, express or implied, about the completeness, accuracy, reliability, suitability, or availability of the information, products, services, or related graphics contained on this website for any purpose.
				</p>
				<p>
					The content on Akboheim is provided for general informational and educational purposes only. It is not intended to be a substitute for professional advice in any field, including but not limited to legal, financial, medical, literary, or educational advice. Always seek the advice of qualified professionals regarding any specific questions or concerns you may have.
				</p>
				<p>
					Any reliance you place on the information found on this website is strictly at your own risk. In no event will Akboheim be liable for any loss or damage, including without limitation, indirect or consequential loss or damage, or any loss or damage whatsoever arising from loss of data or profits arising out of, or in connection with, the use of this website.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section id="book-reviews-and-literary-content">
				<h2>BOOK REVIEWS AND LITERARY CONTENT</h2>
				<p>
					Akboheim publishes book reviews, literary criticism, and cultural commentary. Book reviews and literary opinions are subjective and reflect the personal views of the individual authors. We do not guarantee that you will agree with or enjoy any book, film, or cultural work reviewed on our website.
				</p>
				<p>
					Book cover images, author photographs, and excerpts used in our reviews are generally used under the doctrine of fair use for purposes of criticism, comment, and news reporting. If you are a rights holder and believe your material has been used improperly, please contact us immediately.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section id="educational-content">
				<h2>EDUCATIONAL CONTENT</h2>
				<p>
					Our educational articles and resources are designed to provide general information on various topics related to literature, culture, history, and the arts. This content is not intended to replace formal education or professional instruction. We encourage readers to verify information and consult with educators or experts in specific fields.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section id="external-links">
				<h2>EXTERNAL LINKS</h2>
				<p>
					Through this website, you may be able to link to other websites which are not under the control of Akboheim. We have no control over the nature, content, and availability of those sites. The inclusion of any links does not necessarily imply a recommendation or endorse the views expressed within them.
				</p>
				<p>
					Every effort is made to keep the website up and running smoothly. However, Akboheim takes no responsibility for, and will not be liable for, the website being temporarily unavailable due to technical issues beyond our control.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section id="copyright-and-intellectual-property">
				<h2>COPYRIGHT AND INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY</h2>
				<p>
					All original content published on Akboheim, including articles, essays, images, and graphics created by our team, is the property of Akboheim unless otherwise noted. Unauthorized use and/or duplication of this material without express and written permission from this site's author and/or owner is strictly prohibited.
				</p>
				<p>
					Excerpts and links may be used, provided that full and clear credit is given to Akboheim with appropriate and specific direction to the original content.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section id="user-comments-and-contributions">
				<h2>USER COMMENTS AND CONTRIBUTIONS</h2>
				<p>
					Akboheim welcomes comments and contributions from readers. However, we are not responsible for the content of user comments. The views expressed in comments belong to the individuals who post them and do not necessarily reflect the views of Akboheim.
				</p>
				<p>
					We reserve the right to moderate, edit, or remove any comments that we determine to be inappropriate, offensive, spam, or in violation of our Terms of Service.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section id="errors-and-omissions">
				<h2>ERRORS AND OMISSIONS</h2>
				<p>
					We strive to ensure that all information on our website is accurate. However, errors and omissions may occur. We reserve the right to correct any errors, inaccuracies, or omissions and to change or update information at any time without prior notice.
				</p>
				<p>
					We apologize for any inconvenience caused by errors and appreciate our readers bringing such issues to our attention.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section id="changes-to-this-disclaimer">
				<h2>CHANGES TO THIS DISCLAIMER</h2>
				<p>
					We may update this Disclaimer and Editorial Disclosure from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new disclaimer on this page and updating the "Last Updated" date. You are advised to review this Disclaimer periodically for any changes.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section id="contact-us">
				<h2>CONTACT US</h2>
				<p>
					If you have any questions about this Disclaimer and Editorial Disclosure, please contact us:
				</p>
				<address>
					<strong>Akboheim</strong><br>
					Miami, Florida<br>
					Email: <a href="mailto:contact@akboheim.com">contact@akboheim.com</a><br>
					Phone: 323-941-4865
				</address>
			</section>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.page-container {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 40px 24px;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: #1a1a1a;
	}

	.page-header {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 48px;
		padding-bottom: 24px;
		border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
	}

	.page-header h1 {
		font-family: 'Playfair Display', 'Georgia', 'Times New Roman', serif;
		font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 48px);
		font-weight: 900;
		letter-spacing: -0.03em;
		margin: 0 0 16px;
		color: #1a1a1a;
	}

	.last-updated {
		font-size: 14px;
		color: #666;
		margin: 0;
		font-style: italic;
	}

	.page-content {
		font-family: 'Crimson Text', 'Georgia', serif;
		font-size: 17px;
	}

	.page-content p {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.page-content a {
		color: #8b0000;
		text-decoration: underline;
		text-underline-offset: 2px;
	}

	.page-content a:hover {
		color: #a52a2a;
	}

	.page-content h2 {
		font-family: 'Playfair Display', 'Georgia', 'Times New Roman', serif;
		font-size: clamp(24px, 4vw, 32px);
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
		margin: 2.5rem 0 1.5rem;
		color: #1a1a1a;
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.page-content h3 {
		font-family: 'Playfair Display', 'Georgia', 'Times New Roman', serif;
		font-size: clamp(20px, 3.5vw, 24px);
		font-weight: 600;
		letter-spacing: -0.01em;
		margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
		color: #333;
	}

	.page-content h4 {
		font-family: 'Playfair Display', 'Georgia', 'Times New Roman', serif;
		font-size: clamp(18px, 3vw, 20px);
		font-weight: 600;
		margin: 1.5rem 0 0.75rem;
		color: #444;
	}

	.page-content ul,
	.page-content ol {
		padding-left: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.page-content li {
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.page-content address {
		font-style: normal;
		line-height: 1.8;
		margin: 1.5rem 0;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background: rgba(248, 248, 248, 0.5);
		border-left: 4px solid #8b0000;
		border-radius: 4px;
	}

	.page-content address strong {
		color: #1a1a1a;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.page-container {
			padding: 24px 16px;
		}

		.page-header {
			margin-bottom: 32px;
		}

		.page-header h1 {
			margin-bottom: 12px;
		}

		.page-content {
			font-size: 16px;
		}

		.page-content h2 {
			margin: 2rem 0 1.2rem;
		}

		.page-content h3 {
			margin: 1.5rem 0 0.8rem;
		}

		.page-content address {
			padding: 1rem;
		}
	}
</style>
